{"tid":2042201,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【國安法】太古40年老人區大劈價了","createTime":"2020-05-29T17:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T17:45:27.000Z","uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc444501859a98ecd70135ccfc611a35ccd16ad","tid":2042201,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"早前盛傳以天價成交的鰂魚涌太古城海景單位，土地註冊處顯示，單位最終落實以4,030萬元售出，呎價仍高見3.16萬元，無論售價及呎價均創屋苑新高。<br />\n成交單位為春櫻閣頂層連天台戶（屬屋苑複式戶），實用面積1,277平方呎，早前曾一度盛傳以4,600萬獲買家洽購，據土地註冊處顯示，單位最終落實以4,030萬元售出，呎價31,558元。單位內櫳十分殘舊，相信今次買家亦要為單位進行大進修。<br />\n單位由收租集團永倫持有，早於1986年以175萬購入，一直作長綫收租用，持貨34年，易手帳面獲利3,855萬元。<br />\n據了解，上一宗複式戶成交於2016年錄得，當時銀栢閣連天台戶以2,800萬元易手，面積同屬1,277呎，今次成交價比上一次高出逾4成。<br />\n<br />\n向上劈"},{"pid":"d43fd8de68ba7cde8128446b3f094a0f1e80029a","tid":2042201,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb90bacefe4c1babc206abe1935b92956a2b6687","tid":2042201,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"單位內櫳十分殘舊，相信今次買家亦要為單位進行大進修。<br />\n<br />\n都仲賣到呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靚裝修既話幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c17cf33df1acfd1cd22ef3ba45d262136ccbf34","tid":2042201,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb90bacefe4c1babc206abe1935b92956a2b6687","tid":2042201,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"單位內櫳十分殘舊，相信今次